<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA521_07_IH_0001</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <script src="../../common_practice/js/ema521_01_ih.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema521_07.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema521_07_ih_0001">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="1">
          <span lang="y">반올림하여 나타낸 수에 <span class="ico_round"></span></span>
          <span lang="y">표 하세요.</span>
        </h2>
      </section>
      <section class="contents">
        <div class="boolean_wrap justify_center">
          <div class="boolean_row">
            <div class="text">
              <p lang="y">581을 반올림하여 십의 자리까지 나타낸 수</p>
            </div>
            <div class="boolean_box">
              <span>(</span>
              <button type="button" data-answer-single="true">580</button>
              <button type="button" data-answer-single="false">590</button>
              <button type="button" data-answer-single="false">600</button>
              <span>)</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="boolean_wrap justify_center">
          <div class="boolean_row">
            <div class="text">
              <p lang="y">1472를 반올림하여 백의 자리까지 나타낸 수</p>
            </div>
            <div class="boolean_box">
              <span>(</span>
              <button type="button" data-answer-single="false">1400</button>
              <button type="button" data-answer-single="true">1500</button>
              <button type="button" data-answer-single="false">1600</button>
              <span>)</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p lang="y">
                  581의 일의 자리 숫자가 1이므로 버림하여 십의 자리까지 나타내면 580입니다. <br />
                  1472의 십의 자리 숫자가 7이므로 올림하여 백의 자리까지 나타내면 1500입니다.
                </p>
                <p class="text_label">
                  <span class="label important" lang="y">중요</span>
                  <span lang="y">반올림은 구하려는 자리 바로 아래 자리의 숫자가 0, 1, 2, 3, 4이면 버리고, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9이면 올려서 나타내는 방법입니다.</span>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <!-- <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button> -->
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
